DESCRIPTION 
===========

        Job Monarch is a set of tools to monitor batch jobs on a website.

	This is achieved as a addon to Ganglia.

	Job Monarch consists of three parts:

	*	jobmond)

		* Reports job statistics through Ganglia's gmetric/gmond

	*	jobarchived)

		* Optional
		* Allows the archiving of jobs statistics in a database and more detailed
		  RRDs, with the purpose of providing users or admins with the ability to
		  lookup a node's behaviour and environment at the time of a finished job.

	*	web)

		* Frontend that displays the statistics in a intuitive manner

WEBSITE
=======

For more details, go to the project website:

	* https://subtrac.sara.nl/oss/jobmonarch
